&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;NISC exists to serve our Members and help them serve their communities through our innovative software products, services and outstanding customer support.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
